{"tid":1764742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正聲明：唔好再攞人數嚟判定香港人仲有冇心搞革命","createTime":"2019-12-01T10:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:20:50.000Z","uid":22796,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bb428088ed390dfa76754a7da5ad47221274135b","tid":1764742,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"當初又係連登仔要求全民勇武<br />\n每次個場面好似唔夠和理非 就開始狂屌唔夠人<br />\n我唔知呢班係負面撚分化撚定冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用今日為例 明明今日根本好撚多人 香港人團革命火根本冇熄<br />\n我今日都走撚足三場 上到嚟仲見到有人話唔夠人真係想問佢有冇落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實黑警去到今時今日已經無計可施 <br />\n前線黑警只會用殺人武力同鳩拉嚟傷害手足<br />\n曱甴王鄧炳強淨係識出口術話民意逆轉 老實講我覺得佢真係繼林鄭之後又有一焦土王嚟 用言論團結香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要贏 除咗毋忘初心 仲要睇實身邊嘅手足 唔好令佢哋警入黑警手中<br />\n<br />\n總有一日 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲底要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"486c7f487baeddc42a34dfbfcad30b1584becb44","tid":1764742,"uid":337761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"外媒記者有報<br />\n今日警察向和平示威者噴胡椒tg<br />\n快啲推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入 －》<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=980be118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"30af18b921333eea2172d1058bc5b51826daf356","tid":1764742,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"486c7f487baeddc42a34dfbfcad30b1584becb44","tid":1764742,"uid":337761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"外媒記者有報<br />\n今日警察向和平示威者噴胡椒tg<br />\n快啲推上國際<img src=\"/asse